{"tid":808357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿富汗青年在荷蘭刺傷美國人因認定伊斯蘭教受侮辱","createTime":"2018-09-06T09:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T05:39:26.000Z","uid":20816,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e56cd811540b402b8b849730a0f353aad7ec3e6","tid":808357,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"一個阿富汗人在荷蘭阿姆斯特丹, 用刀襲擊兩個美國人的案件, 調查人相信, 疑犯行兇是他認為伊斯蘭教在荷蘭受到侮辱.<br />\n        案發在星期五, 該名19歲青年乘搭火車到達阿姆斯特丹的車站後行兇, 荷蘭調查人員表示, 兩個美國人被刺傷, 並非因為他們的國籍, 而是疑犯對荷蘭的怨憤. 根據疑犯的口供, 他認定先知穆罕默德, 可蘭經, 伊斯蘭教和真主阿拉, 在荷蘭一再受到侮辱. 疑犯特別提到一個荷蘭國會議員的名字, 該議員經常猛烈批評伊斯蘭教. 調查人員判定, 疑犯行兇是有恐怖主義動機, 去荷蘭是要犯案.<br />\n        較早時, 德國當局表示, 該阿富汗人曾申請庇護, 沒有被德國視為構成安全威脅.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20180904044013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20180904044013&d=cDinVvufwTKkQuZWXBaguIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=b40267a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20180904044013</a>"},{"pid":"3bca76ad0675b9de37005819cc800f1cd72f54db","tid":808357,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bde2c8adc06b7ab30ef4958a66227adfb1f9332","tid":808357,"uid":58022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:15:44.000Z","msg":"發神經,<br />\n咁咪走囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6575f65acd15622c1a7c9423107ad4409117e52e","tid":808357,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bde2c8adc06b7ab30ef4958a66227adfb1f9332","tid":808357,"uid":58022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:15:44.000Z","msg":"發神經,<br />\n咁咪走囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"回教徒侮辱保羅、話耶穌唔係主就得，人哋話佢個穆罕默德就要殺人放火"},{"pid":"423e9f